  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.1">
<l>tiruttāy cempōttē</l>
<l>tirumāmakaḷ taṉkaṇavaṉ</l>
<l>maruttār tolpukaḻ mātava ṉaivarat</l>
<l>tiruttāy cempōttē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Summon [him], crow pheasant;</l>
<l>The beloved of Tiru - the great goddess,</l>
<l>Mādhava of ancient fame and fragrant garlands,</l>
<l>Summon [him] to come, crow pheasant!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
